# Harden.preset - hardening pass for a standalone laptop.
# Parallels Default.preset. One function name per line; lines beginning with #
# are ignored. Only RequireAdmin (first) and WaitForKey (last) are order-sensitive.
#
# To run audited Disassembler cleanup in the same pass, add those function names
# in the CLEANUP block so they execute before the lockdown. Do not load
# Default.preset itself alongside this one - see README.

RequireAdmin

# --- CLEANUP (audited Disassembler tweaks run here, before lockdown) ---

# --- HARDENING ---
LockUSBToWhitelist
DisableWireless
DisableBluetooth
DisablePrivacyExperienceOnLogon
SetupAccountSeparation
HardenUAC
EnableFirewallStrict

HardenVerify
WaitForKey
